      "comment": "TRIZLA (1) is a sprinter who excels over the short dashes. Finished second latest over 350m at this track (20.23) in a Grade 5. Has a strong record here at this journey including four wins. The form out of his last race has been franked. Ready to find winning form. RAPID LULU (3) turned in a solid run fresh when finishing in the placings at this track in a Grade 5 (20.34). Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Expected to be in this for a long way. FIGHTING FAIR (2) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish third (20.30) at this track in a Grade 5 over 350m. Has good early burn and is drawn to be prominent. Expecting another good run. RUDOLF RUMBLE (8) is a last start winner from this box with strong prospects.",
